{
  "stem": "21731.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was a good hiding place for Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were usually blackmailed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, after they had nothing more to pay or had nothing more to give, they were [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] denounced.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Denounced to Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and then that was-- a lot of Poles did that, and Jews did that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stemahovksa certainly did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after that, life went on as usually, with all the terrible things which happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew, because Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Stelmachowska had a radio-- I never listened to it-- but she knew that the Germans are on the-- on the go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every time it was, they took on new positions, they strengthened their positions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we knew what that means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That means back, back, back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was with my-- what my mother used to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hitler will swallow too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He will have to spit it out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went too far.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He went up to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, the Germans-- the Russians came near Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the Poles-- that was already summer, '44.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Warsaw Uprising started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One day suddenly everybody had rifles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Stelmachowska had lots of rifles hidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's why she was not-- well, she was-- would have been killed for the rifles or for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was brave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She didn't mind, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was working for the underground like mad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later I heard from Wisza and from Ola that she had two Englishmen for a while, and this-- later Wisza met here in London when she visited me, one of this Englishman who was hidden there for a while, who was-- came from a prisoner camp, escaped from a German prisoner camp and came to her.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that-- she was a brave woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
